snippet.title: Revita - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1175460/Revita/

A fast paced twin-stick roguelite platformer. Climb an ominous clock tower in a series of procedural encounter rooms and past challenging boss fights on your way to reclaiming your lost memory.

Discord: https://discord.gg/revita
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RevitaGame

Developed by: https://twitter.com/BenstarDEV
